name: Commmando Strike Ops : Gun Shooting VR
summary: Step into the boots of an elite operative in Commando Strike Ops, a groundbreaking tactical FPS designed. This immersive Military Sim challenges you with intense Mission-Based combat against ruthless enemies who will stop at nothing. Customize your weapons with Large Decals & red laser sight. Outsmart & outshoot these relentless enemies in desperate fight for survival where every decision carries weight. This is the definitive Action VR Shooter experience—where your skill decides mission's fate.
